ce\": \"I wanted to be a designer, but I stopped enjoying it, so I sang,\\\" she told the outlet.\", \"from\": 2782, \"to\": 2868, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a designer\", \"from\": 2797, \"to\": 2807}, {\"ngram\": \"the outlet\", \"from\": 2857, \"to\": 2867}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nakamura also spoke more about it in an interview withVogue France.\", \"from\": 2870, \"to\": 2937, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2930, \"end\": 2936, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"score\": 0.9999991122094192, \"rank\": 8.859324563859487e-07, \"text\": \"France\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/France\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nakamura\", \"from\": 2870, \"to\": 2878}, {\"ngram\": \"an interview withVogue\", \"from\": 2907, \"to\": 2929}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said, \\\"When I was younger, I studied pattern making and I really wanted to be a pattern maker.\", \"from\": 2939, \"to\": 3037, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"pattern making\", \"from\": 2980, \"to\": 2994}, {\"ngram\": \"a pattern maker\", \"from\": 3021, \"to\": 3036}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It takes so much patience, though, and that's not my forte.\", \"from\": 3038, \"to\": 3097, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"so much patience\", \"from\": 3047, \"to\": 3063}, {\"ngram\": \"my forte\", \"from\": 3088, \"to\": 3096}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I quit in spite of myself simply because I could not.\", \"from\": 3098, \"to\": 3151, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"spite\", \"from\": 3108, \"to\": 3113}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That was my closest relationship with fashion.\\\"\", \"from\": 3152, \"to\": 3199, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my closest relationship\", \"from\": 3161, \"to\": 3184}, {\"ngram\": \"fashion\", \"from\": 3190, \"to\": 3197}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nakamura understands that she's become an empowering role model for women.\", \"from\": 3201, \"to\": 3275, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Nakamura\", \"from\": 3201, \"to\": 3209}, {\"ngram\": \"an empowering role model\", \"from\": 3240, \"to\": 3264}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 3269, \"to\": 3274}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"At the beginning of my career, I was rather skeptical about this idea of \\u200b\\u200ba role model.\", \"from\": 3277, \"to\": 3366, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the beginning\", \"from\": 3281, \"to\": 3294}, {\"ngram\": \"my career\", \"from\": 3298, \"to\": 3307}, {\"ngram\": \"this idea\", \"from\": 3338, \"to\": 3347}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u200b\\u200ba role model\", \"from\": 3351, \"to\": 3365}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it is a reality: I have influence,\\\" she toldCB News.\", \"from\": 3367, \"to\": 3423, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a reality\", \"from\": 3377, \"to\": 3386}, {\"ngram\": \"influence\", \"from\": 3395, \"to\": 3404}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"If I allow, through my work and my commitments, certain women to assert themselves, then it is a source of pride!\", \"from\": 3424, \"to\": 3538, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my work\", \"from\": 3445, \"to\": 3452}, {\"ngram\": \"my commitments\", \"from\": 3457, \"to\": 3471}, {\"ngram\": \"certain women\", \"from\": 3473, \"to\": 3486}, {\"ngram\": \"a source\", \"from\": 3520, \"to\": 3528}, {\"ngram\": \"pride\", \"from\": 3532, \"to\": 3537}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I believe that influence must be useful.\", \"from\": 3539, \"to\": 3579, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"influence\", \"from\": 3554, \"to\": 3563}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Otherwise it is useless.\\\"\", \"from\": 3580, \"to\": 3605, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"When asked about her commitments, she said she's really taken a liking to women's emancipation.\", \"from\": 3607, \"to\": 3702, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her commitments\", \"from\": 3624, \"to\": 3639}, {\"ngram\": \"a liking\", \"from\": 3669, \"to\": 3677}, {\"ngram\": \"women's emancipation\", \"from\": 3681, \"to\": 3701}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Women's emancipation.\", \"from\": 3704, \"to\": 3726, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"\\\"Women's emancipation\", \"from\": 3704, \"to\": 3725}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That's my fight,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 3727, \"to\": 3754, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my fight\", \"from\": 3734, \"to\": 3742}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It's all violence against women that I fight.\", \"from\": 3756, \"to\": 3802, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"violence\", \"from\": 3766, \"to\": 3774}, {\"ngram\": \"women\", \"from\": 3783, \"to\": 3788}]}, {\"sentence\": \"If I can use my music and my fame for them, I never hesitate,\\\" she added.\", \"from\": 3803, \"to\": 3876, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my music\", \"from\": 3816, \"to\": 3824}, {\"ngram\": \"my fame\", \"from\": 3829, \"to\": 3836}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Joyann Jeffrey is a trending news reporter based in New York City \\u00a9 2025 NBCUniversal Media, LLCApple\\u00ae, Apple logo\\u00ae and App Store\\u00ae are registered trademarks of Apple Inc.\", \"from\": 3878, \"to\": 4049, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3885, \"end\": 3892, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pinus_jeffreyi\", \"score\": 0.5623991977602881, \"rank\": 0.6648944910857081, \"text\": \"Jeffrey\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pinus_jeffreyi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Pinus_jeffreyi\"}, {\"begin\": 3930, \"end\": 3943, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 9.073895043499633e-15, \"text\": \"New York City\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}, {\"begin\": 3983, \"end\": 3988, \"title\": 